column16: Alex Gordon singles on a ground ball to center fielder Byron Buxton.
Kendrys Morales out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Max Kepler.   Eric Hosmer scores.
Eric Hosmer triples (1) on a fly ball to left fielder Eddie Rosario.   Lorenzo Cain scores.

Mike Moustakas flies out to left fielder Eddie Rosario.
Eric Hosmer strikes out on a foul tip.
Alcides Escobar flies out to right fielder Miguel Sano.
Paulo Orlando singles on a soft ground ball to shortstop Eduardo Escobar.
Omar Infante singles on a ground ball to center fielder Byron Buxton.
